{"ID":270202, "Text":"<div class=\"page\"><div class=\"pageNum\"><a name=\"202\"><\/a><div class=\"prev\"><a href=\"stpjs201.html\">Prev<\/a><\/div><div class=\"next\"><a href=\"stpjs203.html\">Next<\/a><\/div>\n\t\t\t    STPJS 202<\/div>\n  <p class=\"cont\">out iniquity;<span class=\"footRef\">1<\/span> said they must be extremely careful in all their examinations, or the consequences\n  would be serious.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">All difficulties which might and would cross our way must be surmounted. Though the soul be\n  tried, the heart faint,<span class=\"footRef\">2<\/span> and the hands hang down,<span class=\"footRef\">3<\/span> we must not retrace out steps; there must be\n  decision of character, aside from sympathy. When instructed, we must obey that voice,<span class=\"footRef\">4<\/span> observe the\n  laws<span class=\"footRef\">5<\/span> of the Kingdom of God,<span class=\"footRef\">6<\/span> that the blessings of heaven may rest down upon us.<span class=\"footRef\">7<\/span> All must act\n  in concert,<span class=\"footRef\">8<\/span> or nothing can be done, and should move according to the ancient Priesthood; hence the\n  Saints should be a select people,<span class=\"footRef\">9<\/span> separate<span class=\"footRef\">10<\/span> from all the evils of the world&mdash;choice, virtuous, and\n  holy. The Lord was going to make of the Church of Jesus Christ a kingdom of Priests,<span class=\"footRef\">11<\/span> a holy\n  people,<span class=\"footRef\">12<\/span> a chosen generation,<span class=\"footRef\">13<\/span> as in Enoch&rsquo;s day,<span class=\"footRef\">14<\/span> having all the gifts as illustrated to the Church\n  in Paul&rsquo;s epistles and teachings to the churches in his day<span class=\"footRef\">15<\/span>&mdash;that it is the privilege of each member\n  to live long and enjoy health. He then blessed the Saints.<span class=\"footRef\">16<\/span> (March 30, 1842.) DHC 4:570.<\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">&ldquo;Try the Spirits&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">17<\/span><\/div>\n  <div class=\"topic centerEmphasis\">The Prophet&rsquo;s Editorial in the Times and Seasons<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">Recent occurrences that have transpired amongst us render it an imperative duty<span class=\"footRef\">18<\/span> devolving\n  upon me to say something in relation to the spirits by which men are actuated.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">It is evident from the Apostles&rsquo; writings, that many false spirits existed in their day, and had\n  &ldquo;gone forth into the world,&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">19<\/span> and that it needed intelligence which God alone could impart to detect\n  false spirits,<span class=\"footRef\">20<\/span> and to prove what spirits were of God.<span class=\"footRef\">21<\/span> The world in general have been grossly\n  ignorant in regard to this one thing, and why should they be otherwise&mdash;for &ldquo;the things of God\n  knoweth no man, but the Spirit of God.&rdquo;<span class=\"footRef\">22<\/span><\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">The Egyptians were not able to discover the difference between the miracles of Moses and those\n  of the magicians until they came to be tested together;<span class=\"footRef\">23<\/span> and if Moses had not appeared in their\n  midst, they would unquestionably have thought that the miracles of the magicians were performed\n  through the mighty power of God,<span class=\"footRef\">24<\/span> for they were great miracles that were performed by them&mdash;a\n  supernatural agency was developed, and great power manifested.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"wideEllipse\">* * *<\/p>\n\n  <p class=\"std\">It would have been equally as difficult for us to tell by what<\/p>\n  <div class=\"footnotes\">\n    <div class=\"footnote\">1. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113788\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113788)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113788)\">D&amp;C 43:11<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">2. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107327\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107327)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107327)\">Jer. 8:18<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">3. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110307\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110307)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110307)\">Heb. 12:12<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114578\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114578)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114578)\">D&amp;C 81:5<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">4. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106052\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106052)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106052)\">Gen. 27:8<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107698\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107698)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107698)\">Zech. 6:15<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110927\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110927)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110927)\">1 Ne. 4:18<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116444\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116444)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116444)\">D&amp;C 132:53<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">5. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106828\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106828)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106828)\">Ps. 105:45<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111147\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111147)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111147)\">2 Ne. 5:10<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113771\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113771)\